data.description: 4 Bedroom / 3 Bath full brick home in Crowne Pointe Subdivision! The interior of this home features wood flooring and gas log fireplace in the living room, wood flooring and granite counters in the eat in kitchen, wood flooring in the dining room, master bedroom with two walk-in closets and glamour bath, new carpet in all 4 bedrooms, large bonus room upstairs with walk-in closet, and a separate laundry room with mud sink. Outdoor amenities include a covered front porch, exposed aggregate driveway, two car attached garage with side entry, and a concrete patio with a hot tub, outdoor kitchen, and fireplace. This home is in a very convenient location to I-65.
